OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBlustery
OL,6,Fshowers will clear back to the
OL,7,Fnorthwest during the evening. Becoming
OL,8,Fdry overnight with increasing clear
OL,9,Fperiods and winds falling light will
OL,10,Fbring a patchy inland frost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FThe morning will be mostly dry
OL,13,Fwith bright or sunny spells. Cloud and
OL,14,Fscattered showers spread northeast
OL,15,Fduring the afternoon, heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
