OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday morning.
OL,7,FCloud and rain, heavy at times, spread
OL,8,Fnortheast late Tuesday, clearing later
OL,9,FWednesday. Sunny spells and scattered
OL,10,Fshowers from the west Thursday.
